On 3/12/1997 at 12:01 a.m., Mr. Donald R. Duck (Witness 1) saw a white male break the glass of his neighbor's (Jacob Joe) front door.  Mr. Duck placed a 911 call on his cell phone to report the incident.  Within minutes, police arrive at the residence (1 NW Brockway Avenue) to find the subject ransacking the house.  Detective Bond was the responding and arresting officer.  The subject was taken to the Santa Fe Police Department and placed under arrest. An arrest report was filed on 3/12/1997.
